[section {External Modules}]

[para]
This section documents selected external NaviServer modules that are commonly
used together with the core server. External modules are maintained outside
the core NaviServer source tree and may require separate checkout,
compilation, installation, or loading.

[para]
The NaviServer project maintains additional external modules. For the full
list of available repositories, see
[uri https://github.com/orgs/naviserver-project/repositories {the NaviServer project repositories on GitHub}].

[para]
Some external modules are documented in more specific sections when their role
belongs to a larger subsystem. For example, [const nsdbpg] and
[const nsoracle] are external modules, but are documented under
[sectref {Database Configuration}] because they implement database drivers for
the [const nsdb] interface.


[include include/config-parameters-module-nssmtpd.man]
[include include/config-parameters-module-nsstats.man]


